AGED -- REPRICING ADJUSTMENTS TO THE 2009-2013 UNCOMPENSATED CARE REIMBURSEMENT DATA TO REFLECT THE MOST CURRENT RULES 
NOTE 1:  For the months of January to September in 2013, 75% of disproportionate share (DSH)  reimbursements have been repriced to FY 2015 Uncompensated Care (UCP) rules. 
NOTE 2:  For the months of October to December in 2013, the UCP reimbursements (which were made in place of 75% DSH)  have been repriced to FY 2015 UCP rules.
